      "In the decades since, Rubbia has turned much of his formidable energy toward one of humanity's greatest practical challenges, the problem of clean and sustainable energy. He has championed innovative and safer designs for nuclear power and large scale concentrated solar power, served as the head of major research institutions, and been appointed a senator for life in Italy, remaining an influential scientific statesman well into his later years.",
